Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.52,0:29:01.60,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Dare mo min'na uzu-uzu shite 'ru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.52,0:29:01.60,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Todos estamos ansiosos por ir!{\i0}
